text.section:
In addition to the duties set forth elsewhere in this title, the Board shall:
Keep a current list showing all:
Licensed optometrists;
Optometrists who are on inactive status;
Diagnostically certified optometrists;
Therapeutically certified optometrists; and
Optometrists against whom action has been taken under § 11-313 of this title;
Keep a full record of its proceedings; and
Adopt an official seal.
